quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  53,27,"Pellet …ďeen …ďe ngoon…óinaani La'akara ho…ďe innira maleykaaji in…óe rew…ďe."
  53,28,"Woodanaani …ďe ganndal, alah ko…ďr ndewata si wona sikke, pellet sikke nafatae goonga hay hu'unde."
  53,29,"…óuurno oon nduntii…óa jikru amen mbo yi…óah si wona nguurndam aduna."
  53,30,"Ko …óoon ganndal mum en haa…ói, pellet ko Alla …ďuri anndude oon majju…óo laawol makko, ko KaŇčko kadi …ďuri anndude oon peew…óo."
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yo…ďa …ďeen bonnu…ďe ko…ďe mbonni ko, o yo…ďa kadi mo∆ī∆īin…ďe mo∆ī∆īoore."
  53,32,"…ďeen wo…ó…óitotoo…ďe bakkatuuji maw…ói …óin e paŇčkare […ďe paggitotaako] si wonaa tokoosi …óin. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaac…óo yaafuyee. Ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude on gila O pu…ó…óunoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde ngonno…óon fu∆ī∆īannde ka deedi neeniraa…ďe mon. Wota on mantu ko'e mon; ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďren."
  53,33,"E a tinaali …óuurnii…óo oon,"
  53,34,"hino okkira see…óaa, hooti o …óawa?"
  53,35,"Kere o jogi ganndal mbirnii…ói ngal o yi'irta?"
  53,36,"Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e …óeri Muusa …óiin"
  53,37,"e [ka …óeri] Ibraahiima kuu…ďnu…óo [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"won'de woŇčkii [woo] ronndotaako doŇčgal (bakkaat) wo…ókii goo,"
  53,39,"e won'de alanaa ne…ó…óanke, si wonaa ko o golli kon;"
  53,40,"e won'de golle makko …óeen, aray ka yi'ee,"
  53,41,"Refti o yo…ďire …óe njo…ďdi timmundi,"
  53,42,"e wonan'de ko ka Joomi ma woni haattirde ndeen."
  53,43,"e won'de ko KaŇčko woni beltinoowo gullinoowo"
  53,44,"ko KaŇčko kadi woni barooro Wuurnita,"